  V Chin2-kiu2 e5 Thau5-khoe. 
  Lun7 chit hu3 chian3-kah, ti7 chiah-e5 peng e5 phoe e5 lai7-tiong, lan2 i2-keng kang2-kiu3 si3-hang7, chiu7-si7 Io-toa3, Hou7-sim-kiaN3, Oe5 kap Tin5-pai5. TaN kan-ta chhun nng7 hang7, chiu7-si7 Thau5-khoe kap Kiam3. Thau5-khoe si7 sim2-mih8? Seng3-chheh kong2, “Tioh8 nia2-siu7 Chin2-kiu3 e5 Thau5-khoe.” TaN chin2-kiu3 si7 sim2-mih8? Lan2 siong5-siong5 eng7 chit ku3-oe7, m7 chai lin2 bat sio2-khoa2 chu3-i3 ka7 i siuN7, si7 sim2-mih8 i3-su3 mah? Lin2 na7 bo5 beng5-beng5 chai hit e5 i3-su3, lin2 chiu7 long2 boe7 tit thang ti3 chit e5 thau5-khoe. 
  Goa2 beh soat-beng5 chin2-kiu3 e5 i3-su3, te7 it hah8 e5 oe7 chiu7-si7 khah-iaN5 a2-si7 tek-seng3. Tioh8 ti3 tek-seng3 e5 thau5-khoe. Chin2-kiu3 thoat-choe7 si7 sim2-mih8? Kiam2 m7 si7 khah-iaN5 choe7-koa3 mah? Chin2-kiu3 thoat-li7 tui3-tek8 si7 sim2-mih8? Kiam2 m7 si7 khah-iaN5 tui3-tek8 mah? Lang5 siong5-siong5 kong2 chin2-kiu3, ia7 sou2 eng7 e5 i3-su3, chhin-chhiuN7 kan-ta chi2-beng5 chin2-kiu3 leng5-hun5 bian2 loh8 toe7-gek8, thang jip8 thian-kok. An2-ni si7 kan-ta chit8 pou7-hun7 e5 te7 it soe3-e5. Lan2 e5 Chu2 Ia5-sou lai5 se3-kan m7-na7 choe3 an2-ni na7-tiaN7 I lai5 beh kiu3-chou7 hoan7-na7 tui3 I lai5 chhin-kun7 Siong7-te3--e5, kau3 kek8-thau5 e5 ho2. Kiu3-chou7 kau3 kek8-thau5 e5 ho2, an2-ni chiu7-si7 chin2-kiu3, chiu7-si7 tek-seng3. 
  Goa2 ai3 po3 lin2 chai, chit8 e5 Ka-na2-tai7 e5 gin2-na2 ti3 chit e5 thau5-khoe, tui3 che oe7 hou7 lin2 e5 koan-liam7 khah beng5, tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 ti3 chit e5 thau5-khoe. 
  Ui-liam5 si7 Ko-teng2 Hak8-hau7 e5 hak8-seng, tui3 i e5 hiaN e5 kam2-hoa3, in2-chhoa7 i chiu7-kun7 Ki-tok. In nng7 lang5 sui5-si5 ti7 in e5 peng5-iu2 e5 tiong-kan choe3 kang, bo5 ku2 hit sou2-chai7 e5 siau3-lian5 lang5 chiu7 gian2-kiu3 Seng3-chheh, in-ui7 in put-chi2 him-bou7 ai3 kang2-kiu3; ia7 khui ki5-to2-hoe7 in-ui7 in ai3 tit-tioh8 un2-chun2. Lau7-lang5 u7-e5 io5-thau5 kong2, “Chiah-e5 siau3-lian5 lang5 boe7 ku2-tng5 khia7-chai7.” 
  Ui-liam5 thiaN-kiN3 lang5 an2-ni kong2, soa3 chin kiaN-hiaN5. Tui3 i e5 jiat8-sim kap thiaN3-thang3, liam5-piN ui7-tioh8 Chu2 choe3 kang, taN chiah-e5 bo5 ku2 kiam2 beh siau-bo5 mah? I kiam2 beh koh chiau3-ku7 piN3-choe3 leng2-tam7-bo5 oah8-khi3 mah? a2-si7 beh poah8-to2 mah? I na2 siuN7 kha-thau5-u na2 chhoah. 
  Teh siuN7 e5 si5, i choe3 chit8 hang7 u7 ti3-hui7 e5 su7; chiu7-si7 chhin-kun7 Siong7-te3 e5 Oe7. I hian-khui I2-sai3-a e5 chheh, thak8 tioh8 chit8 chat, soa3 tiu5-tu5. “m7-bian2 kiaN, goa2 kap li2 ti7-teh; m7-bian2 giau5-gi5, goa2 si7 li2 e5 Siong7-te3; goa2 tek-khak pi3-iu7 li2; hu5-chhi5 li2; ia7 eng7 gi7 e5 chhiu2 khan li2 ”( I2-sai3-a 41 :10 ). 
  Tui3 chiah-e5 oe7, i e5 cheng-sin5 tit-tioh8 an-cheng7. Hit gou7-hang7 e5 eng3-un2, i sui5-e5 ka7 i khoaN3, kau3 hiah-e5 khui3-lat8 jip8 i e5 sim-sin5. Au7-lai5 ti7 hit chat e5 tiong-kan, tu5-khi3 “Goa2” chit ji7 i2-goa7, pat8 ji7 chhin-chhiuN7 bo5--khi3, kan-ta chit ji7 “Goa2” hian2-chhut chin beng5, ti7 hit e5 tiong-kan na7-tiaN7. 
  I khoaN3 chit ji7 “Goa2” ia7 chai tak8 ji7 long2 si7 chi2-khi2 Siong7-te3 pun2-sin. Tui3 chit ji7 “Goa2” chhe7 tioh8 Siong7-te3, sou2-i2 hou7 i e5 kha-thau5-u chhoah. TaN ti7 I e5 bin7-cheng5 tioh8 si2-bo5? Sou2-i2 Ui-liam5 chiu7 gim5-si, “Tui3 I goa2 tit-tioh8 khah-iaN5, goa2 beh oa2-kho3 I bo5 kiaN: in-ui7 Ia5-ho5-hoa si7 goa2 e5 khui3-lat8, goa2 e5 si; I ia7 si7 chin2-kiu3 goa2-e5”. Che kiam2 m7 si7 chi2-beng5 tek-seng3 mah ? 
  Chhin-ai3 siau3-lian5 e5 peng, taN li2 kiam2 bo5 beng5-pek8, Ui-liam5 tu2-tu2 ti7 kau-chian3 e5 khi2-thau5, chai2-iuN7 ti3 tek-seng3 e5 thau5-khoe mah ? 
  Tai7-pit8 iau2-be7 khi3 kap Kho-li7-a kau-chian3, i tai7-seng ti3 tek-seng3 e5 thau5-khoe. I khoaN3 hit e5 toa7-han3 lang5, ia7 chit8-e7 khoaN3 i e5 Siong7-te3, ti7 i bak8-cheng5 e5 toa7-han3 lang5, soa3 piN3-choe3 soe3-a2-han3. In-ui7 tui3 Siong7-te3 e5 eng5-kng, i iau2-be7 hiat chioh8-thau5 e5 tai7-seng, i chai i tek-khak tek-seng3 ( I Sat-bou2-ni2 17 ). 
  I2-li7-a tai7-seng ti3 tek-seng3 e5 thau5-khoe, chiu7 ka7 A-khap ong5 kong2, “Tioh8 khi2-lai5 lim-chiah8, in-ui7 goa2 u7 thiaN-kiN3 loh8 toa7-hou7 e5 siaN.” Au7-lai5 i peh-chiuN7 soaN-teng2 kiu5 hou7 ak toe7, hit-si5 thiN-nih8 long2 bo5 hun5. Bo5 lang5 thiaN-kiN3 loh8-hou7 e5 siaN, tok8-tok8 I2-li7-a na7-tiaN7. Sian-ti sou2 thiaN-kiN3 e5 siaN, si7 Siong7-te3 eng3-un2 beh loh8-hou7 e5 siaN, I chhim-chai Siong7-te3 e5 khui3-lat8 kap chin-sit8, sou2-i2 i thiaN chit e5 eng3-un2 e5 siaN, tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 hou7 i2-keng teh loh8 e5 khoan2. I eng7 tek-seng3 e5 kha-pou7 peh-chiuN7 soaN-teng2 e5 pang5-keng. I iau2-be7 ki5-kiu5 e5 tai7-seng u7 ti3 tek-seng3 e5 thau5-khoe. 
  Chong2-si7 hit jit8 I2-li7-a m7 na7 u7 eng3 un2 thang hou7 i ho2-taN2 kiu5 tek-seng3. I ti7 Ka-bit8 hian3 sio-che3 u7 tit-tioh8 kam3-lap8. Hit e5 sio-che3 si7 ui7-tioh8 I2-sek-liat8 peh-siN3 hian3--e5, an2-ni chiu7-si7 I2-sek-liat8 peh-siN3 long2 siu7 chiap-lap8, sou2-i2 I2-li7-a oe7 tit ho2-taN2 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 lai5 thoe3 choan5 I2-sek-liat8 peh-siN3 kiu5 loh8-hou7. 
  Chhin-ai3 siau3-lian5 e5 peng, siat-su2 lin2 ai3 oh8, lai5 kiu5 u7 eng3-hau7 e5 ki5-to2, thang choe3 toa7 e5 li7-ek, chhiaN2 gian2-kiu3 I2-li7-a ti7 soaN-teng2 sou2 keng-ke3 e5 kou3-su7, ia7 kiu5 Seng3 Sin5 chi2-si7 li2, tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 kiu5, chhin-chhiuN7 i chit8-iuN7. I beh chiong Siong7-te3 eng3-un2 e5 eng5-kng kap lan2 e5 hian3-che3 e5 kong-hau7 ka7 lin2 kong2; chit pai2 m7 si7 ti7 Ka-bit8 hian3--e5, si7 ti7 Thau5-khak-oaN2 e5 toe7 (Ia5-sou teng3 sip8-ji7-ke3 e5 sou2-chai7 ). Au7-lai5 tu2-tu2 ti7 ki5-to2 e5 khi2-thau5, i beh ka7 li2 ti3 tek-seng3 e5 thau5-khoe. Eng7 chit-e5 ti3 ti7 thau5-khak, lin2 chiu7 oe7 kian-kou3 chin3-cheng5, kau3 tit-tioh8 sou2 kiu5--e5. KhoaN3 I Liat8-ong5 18 :41-46. 
  VI Kiam3. 
  “Seng3 Sin5 e5 kiam3, chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7” ( I2-hut-sou2 6 : 17 ). 
  Lan2 i2-keng kang2-kiu3 Io-toa3, Hou7-sim-kiaN3, Oe5, Tin5-pai5 kap Thau5-khoe. M7 chai lin2 u7 chu3-i3, chai chit gou7 hang7 si7 ti5-hong5 e5 chian3-kah, m7-si7 eng7 chiah-e5 choe3 saN-thai5 e5 ke-si. Chi2-u7 chit8 hang7 si7 saN-thai5 e5 ke-si, chiu7-si7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 Kiam3, chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7. ChhiaN2 khoaN3 Si-phian 149:6-9, chiu7 chai Siong7-te3 e5 peh-siN3 e5 chhiu2, na7 chin-chiaN3 u7 gia5 chit ki kiam3, sit8-chai7 oe7 choe3 chin ki5-iN7 e5 su7. 
  ThiaN3-thang3 e5 soe3-kiaN2 ah, goa2 sia2 chiah-e5 hou7 lin2, in-ui7 lin2 ai3 cheng-chian3 ho2 e5 cheng-chian3, koh ai3 tit-tioh8 khah-iaN5. Thau5 chit8 hang7, lin2 tioh8 ki3-tit chit ki siang-bin7 e5 chian3-khi3 si7 “Seng3 Sin5 e5 Kiam3”. Tok8-tok8 khia7-khi2 ti7 sim-lai7 Siong7-te3 e5 Sin5 chiah oe7 eng7 chit ki kiam3, sui-si7 Seng3-keng ia7 oe7 choe3 lou7-eng7. Siat-su2 Seng3 Sin5 na7 bo5 eng7 Seng3-keng e5 chiuN-chat, ia7 si7 kan-ta piN3-choe3 peng5-siong5 e5 oe7, na7-si7 chit khoan2 chhin-chhiuN7 phou2-thong e5 oe7, tek-khak boe7 choe3 lin2 e5 li7-ek. Lin2 na7 kan-ta eng7 lin2 e5 siaN-seh, chiong chit chat Seng3-keng ka7 lang5 kong2, an2-ni boe7 choe3 in e5 li7-ek. Chong2-si7 li2 teh ka7 lang5 kong2 hit chat e5 si5, na7 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 Seng3 Sin5 chioh li2 e5 chhui3 lai5 kong2, thiaN e5 lang5 chiu7 oe7 tit-tioh8 khui3-lat8, au7-lai5 chiu7 sit8-chai7 oe7 tek-seng3. Seng3 Sin5 kap Sin-niu5 ka7 lang5 kong2 “Lai5 ”, lang5 chiu7 beh thiaN. Chong2-si7 na7 kan-ta Sin-niu5 (chiu7-si7 lin2 kap goa2 ) chau2 chin3-cheng5 ka7 lang5 kong2“Lai5”, ia7 bo5 Seng3 Sin5 saN-kap ti7-teh, an2-ni chiu7 bo5 lang5 beh chu3-i3 (Khe2-si7-liok8 22 :17 ). Lin2 na7 ai3 hak8-sip8 thang eng7 chit ki kiam3 e5 koan5-lek8, chhiaN2 siong5-se3 kang2-kiu3 Siong7-te3 sou2 kong2, lun7 I e5 Seng3 Sin5 e5 su7 : Chim-gian5 1 :23 ; Lou7-ka 11 :13 ; Iok-han7 16 :13, 14. U7 chit8 hang7 chin po2-poe3 e5 ki5-to2, chiu7-si7 Si-phian 45:3. Siat-su2 lin2 na7 ai3 eng7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 choe3 u7 khui3-lat8--e5, chhiaN2 chiong chit hang7 lai5 ki5-to2. 
  Koh chit8 hang7, chiu7-si7 lin2 tioh8 beng5-pek chit ki si7 “siang-bin7” e5 kiam3. Chit8 bin7 si7 chi2-khi2 i3-hiong3 Siong7-te3 e5 khui3-lat8, koh chit8-bin7 si7 chi2-khi2 ti2-tng tui3-tek8 e5 khui3-lat8. Lin2 ai3 tit-tioh8 tek-seng3 e5 ki5-to2 ti7 thiN-nih8 a2-bo5 ? Chit ki kiam3 ti7 lin2 e5 chhiu2, u7 khui3-lat8 thang choe3. 
  Goa2 beh ka7 lin2 kong2, Iok-sa-hoat oa2-kho3 Siong7-te3, lai5 eng7 chit e5 khui3-lat8. Cheng3 peh-siN3 kiaN-hiaN5, ia7 i khia7 ti7 in e5 bin7-cheng5, kiah8-bak8 khoaN3 Siong7-te3 e5 Tian7, kiu5 I po2-hou7 in, in-ui7 u7 toa7 e5 kun-peng teh-beh lai5 kong-kek Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2 (2 Lek8-tai7 chi3-liok8 20 :9-12 ). 
  Thau5 chit8 hang7, lan2 tioh8 chu3-i3, in-ui7 Iok-sa-hoat bat Seng3-chheh. Siat-su2 i na7 m7-bat, i chiu7 boe7 eng7 i. Siat-su2 I Liat8-ong5 poeh chiuN kap kau2 chiuN, i na7 bo5 oan5-choan5 chhim chai, i chiu7 bo5 kiam3 thang eng7. I chai te7 poeh chiuN Sou2-lo5-bun5 sou2 kiu5--e5, lai7-tiong kong2, Peh-siN3 na7 tu2-tioh8 sim2-mih8 tui3-tek8, in tioh8 khia7 ti7 Tian7-cheng5, ti7 hoan7-lan7 e5 si5, tioh8 au5-kio3 in e5 Siong7-te3, I beh thiaN in, ia7 pang-chan7 in. I chai te7 kau2 chiuN si7 Siong7-te3 hian2-hian7 ka7 Sou2-lo5-bun5 kong2, I u7 thiaN i e5 ki5-to2, I u7 hou7 Tian7 chiaN5-seng3, ia7 I e5 bak8-chiu kap sim-koaN beh ku2-tng5 ti7 hia bo5 soah. 
  An2-ni thang chai, Iok-sa-hoat ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 u7 thang oa2-kho3, na7 m7 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 khui3-lat8, chiu7 bo5 sim2-mih8 thang pang-chan7 i. Siong7-te3 ti7 iN7-siong7 e5 tiong-kan, eng7 I e5 eng3-un2 ka7 Sou2-lo5-bun5 kong2, soa3 ki3 ti7 chin-sit8 e5 Seng3-chheh. I ki3-tit Siong7-te3 e5 eng3-un2, lai5 khia7 ti7 Tian7-cheng5, kiu5 Siong7-te3 eng7 I e5 khui3-lat8 ti2-tng chiah-e5 tui3-tek8, kau3 beh soah e5 si5 kong2, “In-ui7 goan2 bo5 khui3-lat8 thang ti2-tng chit e5 toa7 kun-peng, goan2 ia7 m7 chai tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 choe3, goan2 e5 bak8-chiu tok8-tok8 ng3 Li2.” Chiah-e5 oe7 tui3 hit-si5 chiaN5-choe3 hiah-e5 bo5 lang5 thang pang-chan7--e5 e5 po2-poe3. ChhiaN2 lin2 thak8 II Lek8-tai7 chi3-liok8 20 chiuN e5 kou3-su7, ia7 khoaN3 Siong7-te3 e5 khui3-lat8 chaiN2-iuN7 kang3-loh8, thiaN in e5 ki5-kiu5; tai7-seng chiok-hok chiah-e5 ki5-kiu5 e5 peh-siN3, au7-lai5 beh biat8-bo5 in e5 tui3-tek8. Tui3 chit e5 kou3-su7, lin2 chiu7 thang beng5-pek8 chit ki kiam3 kap Siong7-te3 e5 khui3-lat8. 
  Koh khoaN3 Chhong3-se3-ki3 32 : 9-12, ti7 hia Nga2-kok kiaN i e5 hiaN I-so3 e5 kun-peng, sou2-i2 i eng7 Siong7-te3 sou2 eng3-un2-e5 lai5 kiu5. Si-un e5 koan5-leng5 sui5-si5 kang3-loh8 un2-chun2 i, hou7 i e5 hiaN e5 siu7-khi3 siau-bo5, chiaN5 choe3 ho5-ho2. 
  Choe3 lau7-bu2-e5 ia7 si7 teh siong-pi, in-ui7 phaiN2-kui2 in2-iu2 i thiaN3-thang3 e5 kiaN2-ji5, ia7 eng7 se3-kan e5 thiaN3-cheng5 kap m7-sin3 e5 toa7 khui3-lat8, lai5 be5-hek8 i e5 sim-chi3. Choe3 lau7-bu2 bo5 khui3-lat8 thang ti2-tng chit khoan2 hui-siong5 e5 khui3-lat8, chong2-si7 i u7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 kiam3, chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7. I khak-sit8 ki3-tit Siong7-te3 e5 eng3-un2 kong2, “Ia5-ho5-hoa kong2, sui-bong2 chit khoan2 toa7 khui3-lat8 e5 pe2-pak8, ia7 si7 teh-beh thoat-li7, siu7 tui3-tek8 liah8-e5 beh tit-tioh8 chin2-kiu3 : in-ui7 kap lin2 cheng-chian3--e5, goa2 beh kap lin2 cheng-chian3, goa2 beh kiu3 lin2 e5 kiaN2-ji5.” Goa2 iau2-be7 oe7 eng7 sim2-mih8 kiat-ko2 thang ka7 lin2 kong2, chong2-si7 goa2 chai bo5 lun7 sim2-mih8 lang5, na7 chiau3 chit e5 hoat-tou7 ki3-tit Siong7-te3 e5 eng3-un2, tek-khak u7 chit ho7 e5 kiat-ko2, chiau3 I sou2 ka7 lan2 kong2, “Tioh8 lai5 saN-kap pian7-lun7”. 
  Chong2-si7 chit ki kiam3 u7 nng7 bin7 koh chit8 bin7 si7 ti2-tng tui3-tek8 e5 khui3-lat8. 
  Gou7-sun5-choeh hit jit8, Pi2-tek ti7 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2 cheng3 lang5 e5 tiong-kan, i eng7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 kong2-khi2 hou7 lang5 teng3-si2 e5 Ia5-sou. Chit ki kiam3 ti7 i e5 chhiu2 teh ong7, chin kin2 koh u7 khui3-lat8, hit jit8 chhi3-chhak8 hiah-e5 m7-sin3--e5 u7 saN chheng lang5. 
  Hui-lek8 khui-thiah I2-sai3-a2 53 chiuN hou7 Ai-the5-o-pek e5 thai3-kam3 thiaN. Hiah-e5 oe7 chin u7 khui3-lat8, oe7 koaN2-chhut hit e5 ou-bin7 lang5 sim-lai7 e5 ou-am3. 
  Kui2-na7 ni5 cheng5, chit8 e5 chhia-chiang2 ti7 chhia-lai7 teh kiaN5. I siu7-khi3 teh chiu3 choa7, chin chu7-khoa. I ti7 mng5--nih8 tu2-tioh8 chit8 e5 lang5, hit lang5 chai tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 eng7 chit ki kiam3, chiu7 kong2, “Siong7-te3 e5 mia5 m7-thang lam7-sam2 chheng-hou.” Hit e5 chhia-chiang2 sui5-si5 eng7 chin bu2-ban7 bo5 le2 e5 oe7 lai5 in3-tap. Hit e5 lang5 koh kong2, “Lam7-sam2 chheng-hou e5 lang5,u7 choe7 bo5 sia3.” I siu7 chit khoan2 e5 chhi3-chhak8 koh khah siu7-khi3, soa3 koh tit8-tit8 chiu3-choa7, ia7 chhut-lat8 sak chhia-mng5, ham2 tioh8 hit e5 lang5 e5 chhiu2, sou2-i2 huih tui3 chng2-thau5-a2 choaN7-chhut, bak-tioh8 chhia-mng5. Chng2-thau5-a2 e5 siong bo5 ku2 chiu7 ho2, chong2-si7 siu7 hit ki kiam3 sou2 chhak8 e5 siong boe7 ho2. Na2 ku2 chit ki kiam3 e5 chhi3-chhak8 na2 chhim, kau3 chhak8-tioh8 i sou2 siat-tok8 e5 oe7, i2-kip8 ki5-u5 chin-choe7 e5 choe7-ok; in-ui7 ka-ki7 sim boe7 peng5-an, sou2-i2 i tioh8 khi3 ki5-to2 Siong7-te3, chhin-chhiuN7 Po2-lo5 kong2, “Chu2 ah ! Li2 ai3 goa2 chaiN2-iuN7 choe3?” Au7-lai5 i chiaN5-choe3 thih-to7 lai7-bin7 i2-kip8 goa7-ui7 e5 lang5 e5 ho2 bou5-hoan7. Mou5 Kai-sat chit8 pai2 che7 be2-chhia chhut-goa7 e5 si5, i kui2-na7 pai2 liam7 chit8 chat Seng3-keng. Tu2-a2 i beh loh8 chhia e5 si5, chit8 lang5 kiaN5 chin3-cheng5 mng7 i kong2, “Chheng2-mng7 leh, li2 sou2 kong2 e5 Seng3-chheh kiam2 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7? Goa2 m7 sin3”. I beng5-beng5 u7 pi7-pan7 beh kap Mou5 Kai-sat pian7-lun7. 
  Kai-sat chu3-bak8 khoaN3 hit e5 lang5 tiap-a2-ku2. Au7-lai5 chiu7 kong2, “Chheng2-mng7 leh, goa2 siuN7 li2 si7 kun-jin5 houN3 ?” 
  I sui5-si5 in3 kong2, “An2-ni tioh8 lah ”. 
  “Na7-si7 an2-ni, chheng2-mng7 li2, siat-su2 na7 u7 chit8 e5 peng, gia5 chit ki siang-bin7 e5 kiam3, chhak8 jip8 li2 e5 kut-chhe2, hit-si5 li2 kiam2 tioh8 khiam3-eng7 lang5 ka7 li2 kong2 hit ki si7 kiam3, koh si7 siang-bin7-e5 ?” 
  Hit e5 koaN thiaN-kiN3 chit-e5, bak8-chiu khoaN3 ke7, soa3 kiaN5 li7-khui khi3 . 
  Kui2-na7 ni5 au7, i koh tu2-tioh8 Mou5 Kai-sat, ia7 ka7 i seh-sia7. I kong2, “Goa2 chai sit8-chai7 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7,in-ui7 u7 chhi3 chhak8 goa2; chong2-si7 hit-si5 goa2 bo5 ai3 sin3 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7.” 
